Text:
WPA kill.exe does what it says on the tin,
it removes the Windows Activation crap - say you've ran it for 30 days without cracking Activation, the crack will get rid of it.
I had a version that AVG found a trojan in, but I'd ran it previously and had no unusual connections/no adware etc, I'm not sure it's a false positive or not though.

DreamPackPL? no idea
too bad this one is in Soviet
